title: Rune 1.00 full torrent with anti-cd key check
description:
Hey guys. This is a fun game i bought a while back and i just thought i would share. =D sharing is caring so if you download it then please seed it. ill seed with my max upload limit which is not much =[ sorry so please seed it guys. There are instructions in there on how to make it so the game doesnt check for the cd.


the modded ini file is in "MODDED RUNE INI FILE" folder

::::Instructions file contents:::::

INSTRUCTIONS


to be able to play the game without a cd just copy the modded rune.ini file into the runesystem
directory and run the game. you need to replace the old rune.ini. then just run the game and it sould start
with the first time run configuration just like you just installed a fresh copy from the cd. enjoy =] make sure
if you are going to play multiplayer that you change the connection type in the multiplayer >> player tab.



::::::End of instructions::::::

enjoy guys!


-accio5 out.
